  "instructions": [
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine flour, baking powder, honey, maple syrup, balsamic vinegar, eggs, vanilla extract, oil, and orange juice. Mix until smooth.",
    "Fold in chopped fresh fruits (halves) and nuts gently into the batter.",
    "Preheat your pan over medium heat. Grease lightly with oil or butter to prevent sticking.",
    "Pour batter onto heated pan and cook on one side until bubbles appear, then flip using a spatula for even cooking.",
    "For added crunch, cut fruits into thin slices and place them between pancakes before serving."
